<h2>Why Learn JavaScript?</h2>
<p>All web developers must know these 3 languages:
  <ul>
    <li>HTML for web page content</li>
    <li>CSS for web page layout</li>
    <li>JavaScript for web page behavior</li>
  </ul>
This tutorial covers every JavaScript from the original version to the recent updates.</p>

